{"tid":1142512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"舊屋邨急速老化 房署補完即日爛","createTime":"2019-05-07T06:20:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T09:09:01.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dcdfe487bc05019605e4542bddb1e1eb8f40be75","tid":1142512,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T06:20:03.000Z","msg":"不少高齡公屋出現石屎剝落及漏水等問題，對住戶造成嚴重困擾，即使房屋署派員維修，小修小補卻無濟於事，甚至有樓宇要外加工字鐵支撐，又有單位內石屎剝落擊傷小孩，房署仍堅持樓宇結構安全。地區人士及測量師批評，現時每15年才全面勘察屋邨結構是過於僵化，又指「重建高樓齡公共租住屋邨的優化政策」門檻高，高齡屋邨重建無期。<br />\n石硤尾邨第20座住戶張太慨嘆，早前大廈外牆及天台進行裝修工程後，其單位廚廁便出現天花剝落及滲漏，石屎伴石灰時時跌落。該邨落成近40年，近年老化問題嚴重，張太單位曾多次維修，惟問題未見改善，她更指曾在維修完成當日，即再度有石屎剝落。同邨住戶蘇婆婆亦指，其單位亦飽受類似問題困擾，更曾有石屎擊傷當時年僅4歲的孫女。<br />\n社區幹事陳龍傑表示，石硤尾邨第19及20座樓齡高，不少單位出現石屎剝落、漏水及牆壁裂痕等，雖然房署為住戶提供維修服務，但維修後問題不斷復現，令住戶擔心樓宇結構安全，惟署方指樓宇無即時危險，亦遲遲未公布重建計劃。<br />\n上世紀60年代入伙的彩虹邨，部分樓宇外以工字鐵支撐，街坊都擔心樓宇結構安全。居於紫薇樓的英姐亦無奈指，單位內不時有石屎剝落，雖然房署有派員維修，但有時「甩底」，維修工作又「求其」，填補天花石屎後同一位置又會再度剝落。<br />\n黃大仙區議員莫健榮表示，彩虹邨鄰近的大磡邨將於未來數年內落成，他曾向房署提議將彩虹邨居民安置至新建屋邨以開展重建，房署卻未有承諾撥出安置單位，意味彩虹邨重建遙遙無期。<br />\n此外，樓齡逾60年的港島西環邨，部分單位亦有類似問題，中西區區議員陳學鋒亦接獲不少居民求助，他認為房署有責任盡快落實重建計劃以保障居民安全，並非單靠維修紓緩問題。<br />\n房委會發言人表示，曾為上述屋邨勘察，結果樓宇結構均屬安全，故現時未相關重建計劃。該會會按政策和4個基本原則考慮個別高樓齡屋邨是否需要重建，包括樓宇的結構狀況、修葺工程的成本效益、合適的遷置資源及原址重建的潛力；亦會通過「全面結構勘察計劃」確定樓宇至少15年進行的修葺及鞏固工程符合成本效益。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/7dWeNVJHDAOWMD_U1TZNNA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9NTU4/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/aef110dbdf68a47535aa543972f35db9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F7dWeNVJHDAOWMD_U1TZNNA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9NTU4%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Faef110dbdf68a47535aa543972f35db9&h=a998d400&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n公屋老化問題逐漸浮現，令不少住戶叫苦連天。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/I2TlXhLGtRMKpNmhdoleJQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/f7155664b04c1b023db191cb565fa56d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FI2TlXhLGtRMKpNmhdoleJQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Ff7155664b04c1b023db191cb565fa56d&h=53e56d21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n張太單位的天花板維修痕迹處處，但仍未能解決石屎剝落問題。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/KJyU4kj46Mu4t6vnzg71Gw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDA1/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/15a9ea23e3aa32c6184bd4acc4105727\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FKJyU4kj46Mu4t6vnzg71Gw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDA1%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F15a9ea23e3aa32c6184bd4acc4105727&h=704fc4b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蘇婆婆擔心單位安全，剝落的石屎更曾擊傷當時年僅4歲的孫女。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/oAs4y.dEsZU_W3kjRRuf3Q--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDA1/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/0daa7a53b9b576c1d7509abf1675350f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FoAs4y.dEsZU_W3kjRRuf3Q--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDA1%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F0daa7a53b9b576c1d7509abf1675350f&h=7f6cb9b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英姐曾預約維修卻被「甩底」，亦試過完成維修後同一位置不久又要次有石屎掉落。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/DywXASCcwXayL285b.TEVQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDA1/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/37f95f2da6040cc8f4492db5644a693b\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FDywXASCcwXayL285b.TEVQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDA1%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F37f95f2da6040cc8f4492db5644a693b&h=b2419dab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n彩虹邨部分大樓外以工字鐵支撐，令居民質疑樓宇結構是否安全。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/zX5rxwM3cMlxy79p6O23Dg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDA1/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/febdf5fad48e478a3c84beb1eeafde99\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FzX5rxwM3cMlxy79p6O23Dg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDA1%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Ffebdf5fad48e478a3c84beb1eeafde99&h=752bbedd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有西環邨住戶長期受石屎剝落困擾。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ZkFJSG9_qrjxhkplDzqvSQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDA1/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/58a0b703c432f93f023e1e7588987bd7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FZkFJSG9_qrjxhkplDzqvSQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDA1%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F58a0b703c432f93f023e1e7588987bd7&h=d87e937a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n西環邨樓宇內外不難發現裂痕處處。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/RXJkGv00ccHzqjmPch5OzA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/1414812956537618613e8cb1e6f78193\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FRXJkGv00ccHzqjmPch5OzA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F1414812956537618613e8cb1e6f78193&h=6abed15f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳龍傑擔心若石硤尾邨第19及20座需要更長時間才有望重建。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Q.2a8rY_tErNeYKhkbrPgw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDA1/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/c8cf51414bb1e314fc3d1613df13c891\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FQ.2a8rY_tErNeYKhkbrPgw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDA1%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Fc8cf51414bb1e314fc3d1613df13c891&h=bf3fd0a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n莫健榮（右）曾建議安置彩虹邨居民到新建屋邨，以進行重建，但遭房署拒絕。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/xho7UJtXIsQEJoBahJC7LA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDEw/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/2434c4735f680ab635e3b7478e2b97c8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fxho7UJtXIsQEJoBahJC7LA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDEw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F2434c4735f680ab635e3b7478e2b97c8&h=4e36b49f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳學鋒認為房署有責任盡快落實重建計劃以保障居民安全，並非單靠維修紓緩問題。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%8E%A2%E5%B0%84%E7%87%88%EF%BC%9A%E8%88%8A%E5%B1%8B%E9%82%A8%E6%80%A5%E9%80%9F%E8%80%81%E5%8C%96%E3%80%80%E6%88%BF%E7%BD%B2%E8%A3%9C%E5%AE%8C%E5%8D%B3%E6%97%A5%E7%88%9B-032617210.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%258E%25A2%25E5%25B0%2584%25E7%2587%2588%25EF%25BC%259A%25E8%2588%258A%25E5%25B1%258B%25E9%2582%25A8%25E6%2580%25A5%25E9%2580%259F%25E8%2580%2581%25E5%258C%2596%25E3%2580%2580%25E6%2588%25BF%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E8%25A3%259C%25E5%25AE%258C%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2597%25A5%25E7%2588%259B-032617210.html&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HMFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=6681cd85\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%8E%A2%E5%B0%84%E7%87%88%EF%BC%9A%E8%88%8A%E5%B1%8B%E9%82%A8%E6%80%A5%E9%80%9F%E8%80%81%E5%8C%96%E3%80%80%E6%88%BF%E7%BD%B2%E8%A3%9C%E5%AE%8C%E5%8D%B3%E6%97%A5%E7%88%9B-032617210.html</a>"},{"pid":"dba4fa98674a3eeefd5a7db4579f7b467fd48f58","tid":1142512,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T06:22:16.000Z","msg":"公屋就算啦"},{"pid":"45aa693b7d6f78cb3ed6a1bc9b523db8aad567ef","tid":1142512,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T06:25:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有冇人記得玄牛點做？</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e30f997edbd965f01e2dba0d033f555fc2a9b65c","tid":1142512,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T19:45:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e39ddc24372928dead49f50d0b5caf72dd7cc5bb","tid":1142512,"uid":33536,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T20:02:09.000Z","msg":"d人手資源去曬大白象，重咩建丫<br />\n<br />\n擺多十幾廿年可能冧樓添"},{"pid":"d6ddd4ff945cc47344c574ba7c6cd0ecb8de44d7","tid":1142512,"uid":251328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T20:20:01.000Z","msg":"重建後又係派哂俾支那人住，蘇屋邨 牛下 元州邨 長沙灣邨 新石硤尾邨就係例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c486ebff8a5ba7e73975476deb954c801be93f5","tid":1142512,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6ddd4ff945cc47344c574ba7c6cd0ecb8de44d7","tid":1142512,"uid":251328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T20:20:01.000Z","msg":"重建後又係派哂俾支那人住，蘇屋邨 牛下 元州邨 長沙灣邨 新石硤尾邨就係例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T09:09:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}